{
  "stem": "10119.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so my younger sister was with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My parents took the whole family and were hidden.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We also owned property in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we knew somebody who hid my parents, which that's where the tragedy start.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My parents decided they wanted to have the family together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] there was-- they wrote somehow with messenger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they would have [INAUDIBLE], and they stayed over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We had like a bungalow in the country, which we had there a woman and a daughter who took care of our land.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And in the summer, we used to send away there the-- the cows, and she took care of them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They slept over on the-- on the attic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But it's a small town, and word got [? along. ?] They-- there was called a siege.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "When it was already-- I don't know it was the Hungarian or the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They were looking-- they were bounty hunters-- and they were looking for any Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Whoever brought in, they got a nice reward.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Well, it was a very big story [INAUDIBLE], because somebody was caught.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Because that's all what they were carrying is money and jewelry, and they were killed for the money and jewelry.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But my older sister died on the spot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My younger one was-- had a knife through her neck, but she didn't-- she didn't die.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She went into town, and from what I understand, they stripped her naked.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She went down to our neighbor, and they give her a sheet to cover herself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, they called the police.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they knew the people who killed her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The people were arrested.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it cost my family's life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My younger sister was taken to SIghet, Romania to the hospital, and they sewed her throat together.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
